commit.message:
configure.in (m68k-hp-hpux*, [...]): The underscore should have been an hyphen, fixed.

* configure.in (m68k-hp-hpux*, xm_alloca.h): The underscore should
have been an hyphen, fixed.
* configure: Rebuilt.

From-SVN: r30354
